==Demographics==
At the [[2020 United States Census|2020 census]] there were 83 people and 28 households living in the CDP.<ref name="Census 2020"/><ref>{{Cite web| url=https://data.census.gov/cedsci/table?g=1600000US0436780&d=DEC%20Redistricting%20Data%20%28PL%2094-171%29&tid=DECENNIALPL2020.H1| title=Kaka CDP, Arizona: 2020 DEC Redistricting Data (PL 94-171): H1. Occupancy statistics| publisher=U.S. Census Bureau| access-date=May 16, 2022}}</ref>

The median household income was $39,573. The per capita income for the CDP was $13,965.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arizona.hometownlocator.com/az/maricopa/kaka.cfm |publisher=Arizona.hometownlocator.com |access-date=August 24, 2021 |date=2021 |title=Kaka, AZ Profile: Facts & Data}}</ref>

